    <item>
      <title>研究发现，助听器可以延长寿命。但前提是经常使用</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/sections/health-shots/2024/01/04/1222770525/hearing-aids-hearing-loss-longevity-life-span-restoring-hearing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国大约有 4000 万成年人有听力损失，但大多数人不使用助听器。这增加了社会孤立、身体和认知能力下降的风险，并可能导致过早死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/sections/health-shots/2024/01/04/1222770525/hearing-aids-hearing-loss-longevity-life-span-restoring-hearing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 10:00:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
